Well agree that quality/sound is good. 
I never expected the movie to get so sick and twisted though. For a 2hour movie the first hour especially first 10-15min was actually okay/quite good I think. Last hour was just too sick for my taste. Schizophrenic and nausia took over the last hour and sick fetish sex. A shame Michael Biehn was in this movie - that guy in my oppinion belongs to better movies. 
I do however give kudos to some of the other actors (Michael Eklund in particular and Milo Ventimiglia did okay aswell) to play that sick role they actually did gr8. 
I cant however recommend this movie unless you enjoy these type of movies I just described :)
